# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
/coverage

# next.js
/.next/
/out/

# production
/build

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
# .env.example 只是範例(無真實金鑰)，同事 clone 下來要照著它認識格式，必須進版控——
# 不能被這條規則一起擋掉(踩過：.env* 連 .env.example 都一起排除了)。
.env*
!.env.example

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# agent-hub local state (帳密/DB 只留在本機，絕不進版控)
/data/
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
